<div class="title">Pure Euphoria</div>
<div class="substance">Codeine (with Acetaminophen) & Alprazolam</div>
<div class="author">by <a href="/experiences/exp.cgi?A=Search&AuthorSearch=badboy&Exact=1">badboy</a></div>


